1
00:00:04,550 --> 00:00:07,670
You've got a fever. Are you that nervous
about starting work next week?

2
00:00:07,670 --> 00:00:11,140
Hurry up and eat, then get some sleep
so you can get better.

3
00:00:11,140 --> 00:00:12,350
I'm fine.

4
00:00:12,350 --> 00:00:13,850
It's just a mild cold.

5
00:00:16,140 --> 00:00:18,440
Here, open wide. Say, "Ah."

6
00:00:18,440 --> 00:00:21,480
I told you, I don't need help!
I can feed myself.

7
00:00:21,480 --> 00:00:23,440
Come on, open up.

8
00:00:23,440 --> 00:00:25,730
Ahhh.

9
00:00:29,530 --> 00:00:30,160
Is it good?

10
00:00:31,490 --> 00:00:32,200
Yeah, it's good.

11
00:00:33,370 --> 00:00:34,370
What's with you?

12
00:00:34,370 --> 00:00:37,080
Nothing. It's nothing.

13
00:00:37,080 --> 00:00:40,460
Here, eat some more.

14
00:00:42,860 --> 00:00:44,860
- Huh?
- It's delicious!

15
00:00:45,670 --> 00:00:50,740
(First Day of Work - Morning)

16
00:00:50,800 --> 00:00:52,930
Do you want me to help you with your tie?

17
00:00:53,390 --> 00:00:56,060
No, thanks. I can do it myself!

18
00:00:56,060 --> 00:00:59,390
Doesn't grad school
start today too?

19
00:00:59,390 --> 00:01:01,480
I'm all set.

20
00:01:01,480 --> 00:01:04,860
If you don't hurry up,
you'll be late on your first day.

21
00:01:14,370 --> 00:01:17,540
Okay, that should do it.

22
00:01:17,540 --> 00:01:18,500
Aren't you going to say thank you?

23
00:01:18,500 --> 00:01:19,450
Huh?

24
00:01:19,450 --> 00:01:22,960
How about, "Thank you, big brother"?

25
00:01:29,130 --> 00:01:31,670
Thank you, big brother.
I'm off!

26
00:01:36,970 --> 00:01:40,100
I'm Iijima Hinata.
It's a pleasure to meet you.

27
00:01:40,100 --> 00:01:42,730
I'm Iijima Hinata!
It's a pleasure to meet you!

28
00:01:42,730 --> 00:01:45,810
I'm Iijima Hinata...

29
00:01:48,190 --> 00:01:51,400
(Senior Colleague
Kamiki Kyota)

30
00:01:53,360 --> 00:01:55,780
I'm Kamiki. Nice to meet you.

31
00:01:55,780 --> 00:01:58,370
It's a pleasure to meet you.

32
00:02:05,460 --> 00:02:07,540
Hey, you...
